rts are sure to become a staple in your closet, offering endless possibilities for mixing and matching with your favorite pieces. Embrace the spirit of summer with confidence and styleâ€”choose our brown shorts and make a statement wherever you go.</p>', 'simple', '1 item', 87, 129, 12.00, 9.96, 17.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'FASH05', 0, 'in_stock', 'Tan Cargo Shorts', 'Stay comfortable and stylish on sunny days with our Tan Cargo Shorts. Crafted with durable fabric and multiple pockets, they\'re perfect for outdoor adventures or casual outings.', 33, 33, NULL, '7', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'tan-cargo-shorts', 1, 4, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 9, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-25 22:14:38', '2024-06-21 02:18:46'),
(11, 'Chic Mini Dress', 'Elevate your style with our chic mini dress. Effortlessly trendy and versatile, it\'s perfect for any occasion. Flaunt your fashion-forward flair with this must-have piece.', '<p><strong>Introducing our latest creation</strong>: the Chic Mini Dress, a fusion of sophistication and comfort that\'s bound to elevate your style game. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this dress is a testament to timeless elegance. From its flattering silhouette to its impeccable stitching, every aspect of this dress exudes quality and refinement.</p><p>Imagine slipping into this dress and feeling an instant surge of confidence. Its sleek design accentuates your curves, while the mini length adds a touch of flirtatious charm. Whether you\'re attending a cocktail party or a romantic dinner, this dress ensures you\'ll make a lasting impression.</p><p>But it\'s not just about looks; our chic mini dress is designed with your comfort in mind. Made from high-quality, breathable fabric, it feels like a second skin, allowing you to move with ease and grace. Say goodbye to restrictive clothing that leaves you feeling constricted and hello to effortless elegance.</p><p>Versatility is another hallmark of this dress. Pair it with heels and statement jewelry for a formal event, or dress it down with sneakers for a more casual vibe. However you choose to style it, one thing\'s for sure: All eyes will be on you.</p><p>And let\'s talk about the color options. From classic black to vibrant red, there\'s a shade to suit every taste and occasion. Mix and match to create your signature look, or stick to tried-and-true neutrals for a timeless appeal.</p><p>Invest in the Chic Mini Dress and upgrade your wardrobe with a piece that transcends trends. With its impeccable craftsmanship and enduring style, it\'s a wardrobe staple you\'ll reach for again and again. Don\'t settle for ordinary; choose extraordinary with our chic mini dress.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 38, 36, 10.00, 9