(12, 'Boyfriend Shirts', 'Boyfriend shirts are oversized, relaxed-fit shirts originally inspired by men\'s fashion. They offer a comfortable and effortlessly chic look, often characterized by a loose silhouette and rolled-up sleeves. Perfect for a casual yet stylish vibe', '<p><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Boyfriend shirts are a contemporary take on classic men\'s shirts, reimagined for the modern woman. Characterized by their relaxed and oversized fit, these shirts exude a casual yet effortlessly chic vibe. Drawing inspiration from the idea of borrowing clothing from a boyfriend\'s wardrobe, they typically feature a loose silhouette with dropped shoulders and longer hemlines, perfect for achieving that relaxed, borrowed-from-the-boys look.</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:start\"><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Crafted from soft and comfortable fabrics such as cotton or linen, boyfriend shirts offer a luxurious feel against the skin. They often come in a variety of styles, including button-downs, flannels, or denim, offering versatility for different occasions and personal preferences. Rolled-up sleeves and a slightly slouchy fit add to the laid-back aesthetic, making them ideal for casual outings, relaxed weekends, or even as a stylish layering piece.</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:start\"><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">One of the key features of boyfriend shirts is their versatility. They can be styled in numerous ways to suit different looks and moods. For a casual day out, pair them with jeans or leggings for a comfortable yet put-together ensemble. Alternatively, dress them up with a statement belt and heels for a more polished look that effortlessly transitions from day to night.</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:start\"><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><