s sleek and contemporary silhouette instantly captivates, making it a standout piece in any living room or entertainment space. With clean lines and a sophisticated finish, this console exudes elegance and refinement, elevating the aesthetic appeal of your home.\n\nFunctionality is at the forefront of the Eldora TV Console\'s design, offering ample storage options to keep your media essentials organized and easily accessible. Featuring a combination of open shelves and enclosed cabinets, it provides versatile storage solutions for DVDs, gaming consoles, remote controls, and more. The thoughtful layout ensures efficient organization while minimizing clutter, allowing you to create a tidy and inviting entertainment area.\n\nCrafted from high-quality materials, such as solid wood or engineered wood, the Eldora TV Console is built to last. Its robust construction ensures durability and stability, providing a reliable platform for your television and entertainment devices. Additionally, some models may feature additional design elements, such as cable management systems or adjustable shelves, further enhancing the console\'s functionality and versatility.\n\nVersatile and adaptable, the Eldora TV Console seamlessly integrates into a variety of interior decor styles, from sleek and modern to transitional or industrial-chic. Whether used as a standalone piece or paired with other furniture items, it makes a bold statement while offering practical storage solutions. With its timeless design, premium craftsmanship, and thoughtful features, the Eldora TV Console is the perfect choice for enhancing both the aesthetics and functionality of your entertainment space.', 488, 488, NULL, 'your order will deliver within 5 to 10 days', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'eldora-tv-console', 1, 5, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 10, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-07 00:38:43', '2024-05-07 00:48:55'),
(73, 'Mackbook Air', 'A sleek and lightweight laptop with powerful performance, stunning Retina display, and all-day battery life, perfect for productivity on the go.', '<p><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">The MacBook Air is Apple\'s iconic ultraportable laptop, renowned for its sleek design, impressive performance, and exceptional user experience. Designed to be incredibly thin and lightweight, the MacBook Air is the epitome of portability without compromising on power or functionality.</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:start\"><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">At the heart of the MacBook Air is its stunning Retina display, which delivers vivid colors, sharp text, and precise detail for an immersive viewing experience. Whether you\'re browsing the web, watching movies, or editing photos, the Retina display ensures every image is rendered with incredible clarity and precision.</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:start\"><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Under the hood, the MacBook Air is powered by the latest generation of Intel processors, providing lightning-fast performance for everyday tasks and demanding applications alike. From web browsing and document editing to graphic design and video editing, the MacBook Air can handle it all with ease, thanks to its powerful CPU and integrated graphics.</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:start\"><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Despite its compact size, the MacBook Air boasts an impressive array of features and capabilities. From the innovative Touch ID sensor for secure authentication to the spacious trackpad with Force Touch technology, every aspect of the MacBook Air is designed to enhance your productivity and streamline your workflow.</span></span></p><p style=\"text-align:start\"><span style=\"color:rgb(13, 13, 13);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In addition to its performance and features, the MacBook Air also offers exceptional battery life, allowing you to work, play, and create for extended periods without needing to recharge. Whether you\'re on the road or at your desk, the MacBook Air ensures you can stay productive and connected all day long.</span></span></p>', 'simple', '1 Pieces', 5000, 25, 1116.25, 1093.93, 2.50, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ELEC01', 0, 'in_stock', 'Macbook Air', 'The MacBook Air stands as Apple\'s quintessential ultraportable laptop, embodying the pinnacle of design, performance, and user experience. At its core lies an ethos of seamless integration between form and function, resulting in a device that redefines the standards of modern computing.\n\nWith its iconic thin and lightweight design, the MacBook Air offers unparalleled portability without sacrificing power. Its sleek aluminum unibody construction not only exudes elegance but also ensures durability and reliability, making it the ideal companion for users on the move.\n\nThe MacBook Air features a brilliant Retina display that delivers stunning visuals with vibrant colors, sharp details, and true-to-life imagery. Whether you\'re browsing the web, editing photos, or watching movies, every pixel comes to life on the immersive screen, offering an unrivaled viewing experience.\n\nUnder the hood, the MacBook Air is powered by the latest generation of Apple silicon, delivering remarkable performance and efficiency. From everyday tasks like web browsing and email to more demanding endeavors such as photo and video editing, the MacBook Air effortlessly handles it all with ease.\n\nIn addition to its powerful performance, the MacBook Air offers a range of innovative features designed to enhance productivity and user convenience. The Magic Keyboard provides a comfortable and responsive typing experience, whi