(83, 'Sonos Speaker', 'A premium wireless speaker system delivering rich, room-filling sound and seamless multi-room audio synchronization. Perfect for immersive music listening experiences throughout your home.', '<p>The Sonos Speaker redefines home audio with its premium wireless sound system, designed to deliver immersive, high-fidelity audio experiences throughout your living space. With its sleek and modern design, this speaker seamlessly blends into any room while providing rich, room-filling sound that enhances your music listening, movie watching, and gaming experiences.</p><p>Equipped with advanced wireless technology, the Sonos Speaker offers seamless multi-room audio synchronization, allowing you to enjoy synchronized playback of your favorite songs in different rooms of your home. Whether you\'re hosting a party, relaxing in the living room, or cooking in the kitchen, you can create a cohesive audio atmosphere that immerses you in the music wherever you go.</p><p>The Sonos Speaker is more than just a speaker; it\'s a versatile entertainment hub that integrates seamlessly with your favorite streaming services, voice assistants, and smart home devices. With support for popular music streaming platforms like Spotify, Apple Music, and Amazon Music, as well as voice control via Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant, you can easily access and control your music with simple voice commands or the Sonos app. Whether you\'re looking to elevate your listening experience or create the ultimate home entertainment setup, the Sonos Speaker delivers premium sound quality, versatility, and convenience in one stylish package.</p>', 'simple', '1 Pieces', 500, 20, 175.00, 173.25, 1.50, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ELEC10', 0, 'in_stock', 'Sonos Speaker', 'The Sonos Speaker is a pinnacle of audio engineering, offering a premium listening experience that elevates your home entertainment to new heights. With its sleek and minimalist design, this wireless speaker blends seamlessly into any decor, while its powerful sound fills the room with immersive audio. Whether you\'re streaming music, watching movies, or gaming, the Sonos Speaker delivers crystal-clear sound with deep, rich bass and crisp highs, ensuring every note, dialogue, and sound effect is heard with stunning clarity.\n\nOne of the standout features of the Sonos Speaker is its ability to synchronize with other Sonos speakers throughout your home, creating a cohesive multi-room audio system. With Sonos\' proprietary Trueplay technology, each speaker automatically adjusts its audio output to optimize sound quality based on its placement in the room, ensuring consistent and balanced audio no matter where you are. Whether you\'re hosting a party, relaxing in the living room, or unwinding in the bedroom, you can enjoy synchronized playback of your favorite music, podcasts, or audiobooks throughout your entire home.\n\nBeyond its exceptional sound quality and multi-room capabilities, the Sonos Speaker offers seamless integration with popular streaming services, voice assistants, and smart home devices. With support for services like Spotify, Apple Music, and Pandora, as well as voice control via Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant, you can easily access and control your music with simple voice commands or the intuitive Sonos app. Plus, with compatibility with Apple AirPlay 2, you can effortlessly stream audio from your iPhone, iPad, or Mac to your Sonos Speaker with just a tap.\n\nIn addition to its audio prowess, the Sonos Speaker is designed for easy setup and intuitive operation. With the Sonos app, you can quickly configure your speaker, customize settings, and create playlists to suit your preferences. Whether you\'re a seasoned audiophile or a casual music lover, the Sonos Speaker offers a premium listening experience that\'s as effortless as it is immersive, making it the perfect addition to any home audio setup.', 542, 542, NULL, 'your order is deliver within 4 to 8 days', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'sonos-speaker', 1, 6, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 12, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-07 02:32:22', '2024-05-09 22:43:43');
