nnection with nature and promoting mindfulness as you nurture and watch your plant thrive. Its steady growth and evergreen presence serve as a reminder of the beauty and resilience of the natural world, even in the midst of our fast-paced urban lives.</p><p>In summary, the Heartleaf Philodendron is more than just a houseplant; it\'s a green companion that brings joy, tranquility, and health benefits into your home or workspace. Whether you\'re looking to enhance your indoor environment, connect with nature, or simply add a touch of greenery to your life, the Heartleaf Philodendron is sure to charm and delight with its timeless beauty and effortless grace.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 45, 21, 12.00, 7.92, 34.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PLAN15', 0, 'in_stock', 'Heartleaf philodendron', 'Elevate your space with the Heartleaf Philodendron. Lush, low-maintenance, and air-purifying, it adds a touch of green serenity to any room or office. Perfect for plant lovers and beginners alike.', 1236, 1236, NULL, 'our order is likely to reach you within 10 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'heartleaf-philodendron', 1, 13, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-13 21:42:27', '2024-05-13 21:42:27'),
(195, 'Elegant Snake Plant', 'Discover the allure of Dracaena trifasciata, an elegant and low-maintenance addition to any space. Its striking foliage and air-purifying qualities make it a must-have for plant enthusiasts.', '<p>Welcome to the world of Dracaena trifasciata, commonly known as the Snake Plant or Mother-in-law\'s Tongue. This remarkable botanical marvel is not just a plant; it\'s a statement piece for any environment. With its sleek, vertical leaves showcasing variegated patterns of green, yellow, and silver, the Snake Plant adds an air of sophistication to any room.</p><p>But its appeal isn\'t just aesthetic; the Snake Plant is renowned for its air-purifying qualities. NASA\'s Clean Air Study identified it as one of the top plants for improving indoor air quality by removing toxins such as formaldehyde, benzene, xylene, and trichloroethylene. So, not only does it enhance the visual appeal of your space, but it also contributes to a healthier living environment.</p><p>One of the most attractive features of the Snake Plant is its resilience and low maintenance requirements. It thrives in a variety of conditions, tolerating low light and infrequent watering, making it ideal for both novice and experienced plant enthusiasts. Whether you place it in a bright, sun-drenched corner or a dimly lit office cubicle, the Snake Plant will flourish with minimal attention.</p><p>Originating from West Africa, the Snake Plant has a rich cultural history. In traditional folklore, it\'s believed to bring good luck and prosperity to its owners, making it a popular choice for housewarming gifts and office decor. Its upright growth habit symbolizes resilience and endurance, making it a perfect companion for those seeking positivity and strength in their surroundings.</p><p>The versatility of the Snake Plant extends beyond its visual appeal and air-purifying properties. Its architectural form adds dimension and interest to interior landscapes, whether used as a standalone statement piece or incorporated into lush botanical arrangements. From modern minimalist spaces to eclectic bohemian interiors, the Snake Plant seamlessly integrates into a variety of design styles, elevating the ambiance with its natural charm.</p><p>Caring for your Snake Plant is a breeze. Simply place it in well-draining soil and allow the top inch to dry out between waterings. Avoid overwatering, as this can lead to root rot. In terms of light, the Snake Plant is adaptable, tolerating both bright indirect light and low light conditions. Regularly dusting the leaves with a damp cloth not only keeps them clean but also enhances their ability to photosynthesize.</p><p>Whether you\'re a seasoned plant parent or just beginning your greenery journey, the Snake Plant is a must-have addition to your indoor oasis. Its timeless elegance, air-purifying qualities, and ease of care make it a top choice for bringing the beauty of nature indoors. Elevate your space with the understated sophistication of the Snake Plant and experience the transformative power of greenery in your life.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 64, 23, 12.00, 9.24, 23.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'PLAN16', 0, 'in_stock', 'Elegant Snake Plant', 'Discover the allure of Dracaena trifasciata, an elegant and low-maintenance addition to any space. Its striking foliage and air-purifying qualities make it a must-have for plant enthusiasts.', 1240, 1240, NULL, 'our order is likely to reach you within 6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'elegant-snake-plant', 1, 13, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-13 21:45:05', '2024-05-13 21:45:05'),
