(293, 'Dark Chocolate Muesli', 'Dark Chocolate Muesli is a delicious and nutritious breakfast option that combines the richness of dark chocolate with the wholesome goodness of oats, nuts, and seeds. Packed with fiber and antioxidants, it offers a perfect balance of taste and health benefits. Ideal for starting your day with a burst of energy and flavor.', '<p>Dark Chocolate Muesli tantalizes the taste buds with its decadent combination of premium dark chocolate and wholesome ingredients. Crafted with care, this muesli features a medley of rolled oats, crunchy nuts, and plump dried fruits, all generously coated in velvety dark chocolate. Each spoonful is a harmonious symphony of flavors and textures, making breakfast an indulgent yet nutritious affair.</p><p>Beyond its irresistible taste, Dark Chocolate Muesli is a powerhouse of nutrients. Oats provide a hearty dose of fiber, promoting digestive health and providing sustained energy throughout the morning. The inclusion of nuts and seeds adds healthy fats, protein, and essential minerals, while the dark chocolate contributes antioxidants that support heart health and overall well-being.</p><p>Versatile and convenient, Dark Chocolate Muesli can be enjoyed in various ways. Simply pair it with milk or yogurt for a quick and satisfying breakfast, sprinkle it over smoothie bowls for added crunch, or use it as a topping for desserts and baked goods. Whether you\'re fueling up for a busy day ahead or treating yourself to a guilt-free indulgence, Dark Chocolate Muesli offers a deliciously wholesome option to start your day on a sweet note.</p>', 'simple', '1 KG', 1000, 35, 30.00, 26.40, 12.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GYM12', 0, 'in_stock', 'Dark Chocolate Muesli', 'Dark Chocolate Muesli is a delectable fusion of premium ingredients meticulously crafted to elevate your breakfast experience. Indulge in the luxurious combination of dark chocolate with hearty rolled oats, crunchy nuts, and succulent dried fruits, creating a symphony of flavors and textures that delights the senses with every bite. With a balanced blend of sweetness and richness, this muesli transforms ordinary mornings into extraordinary culinary adventures.\n\nWhat sets Dark Chocolate Muesli apart is its nutritional profile, which marries indulgence with health benefits. Oats serve as a fiber-rich foundation, aiding digestion and providing a sustained source of energy to kickstart your day. Meanwhile, the inclusion of nuts and seeds adds a satisfying crunch along with essential nutrients such as protein, healthy fats, and antioxidants. The dark chocolate not only enhances the taste but also contributes antioxidants known to support heart health and cognitive function, making this muesli a nourishing choice for both body and mind.\n\nVersatility is another hallmark of Dark Chocolate Muesli, offering endless possibilities to suit your preferences and dietary needs. Enjoy it with cold milk or yogurt for a quick and satisfying breakfast, or get creative by incorporating it into smoothie bowls, baked goods, or even trail mixes for on-the-go snacking. Its versatility extends beyond breakfast, making it a versatile ingredient for desserts, energy bars, and homemade granola.\n\nWith Dark Chocolate Muesli, you can savor the guilt-free pleasure of indulgent flavors without compromising on nutrition. Whether you\'re fueling up for a busy day or savoring a leisurely morning, this muesli is a delicious and wholesome option that nourishes both body and soul. Elevate your breakfast routine and treat yourself to the luxurious taste of Dark Chocolate Muesli, where decadence meets nutrition in every delightful spoonful.', 1722, 1722, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 3-5 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'dark-chocolate-muesli', 1, 18, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 53, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-21 03:37:05', '2024-05-21 03:37:05'),
(294, 'Precision Injection Solutions', 'Discover our advanced surgical and vaccination syringes, designed for precise, safe, and efficient medical procedures. Crafted with high-quality materials, these syringes ensure accurate dosing and patient comfort.', '<p>Introducing our state-of-the-art surgical and vaccination syringes, meticulously engineered to meet the highest standards of medical excellence. Our syringes are crafted from top-tier, medical-grade materials to ensure durability, precision, and safety in every use. Designed for both surgical procedures and vaccination purposes, they offer unparalleled accuracy and ease of use, making them an indispensable tool for healthcare professionals.</p><p>Our surgical syringes are optimized for precision and control, crucial for delicate operations where accuracy is paramount. The ergonomic design reduces hand fatigue, allowing for more extended periods of use without compromising on performance. Each syringe is equipped with a smooth-glide plunger, providing consistent pressure and minimizing the risk of sudden, unintended movements. This ensures that every milliliter is delivered precisely where needed, enhancing the effectiveness of surgical interventions and patient outcomes.</p><p>For vaccination purposes, our syringes are designed to facilitate swift and efficient administration of vaccines. The ultra-sharp, fine-gauge needles minimize discomfort for patients, making the vaccination process as painless as possible. This is particularly important in mass immunization programs where patient comfort can significantly influence public willingness to participate. The syringes are available in various sizes to accommodate different vaccine volumes, ensuring versatility and adaptability in diverse clinical settings.</p><p>Safety is a top priority in our design philosophy. Each syringe is equipped with safety features to prevent needlestick injuries, a critical consideration in modern healthcare environments. The design includes retractable needles and secure locking mechanisms that activate automatically after use, safeguarding both the healthcare provider and the patient. This feature not only enhances safety but also contributes to reducing the risk of cross-contamination and the spread of infectious diseases.</p><p>Our syringes also feature clear, easy-to-read gradations that enable precise measurement of medication and vaccines, ensuring accurate dosing every time. This precision is vital in both surgical and vaccination contexts, where even slight deviations in dosage can have significant impacts on patient health. The transparency of the syringe barrel allows for easy detection of air bubbles and contaminants, ensuring that only the intended substance is administered.</p><p>In addition to functionality and safety, our syringes are designed with sustainability in mind. The materials used are not only high-quality but also environmentally friendly, reducing the overall ecological footprint of medical waste. By prioritizing sustainability, we contribute to a healthier planet while maintaining the highest standards of medical care.</p><p>Healthcare professionals trust our syringes for their reliability and performance. Whether for intricate surgical procedures or large-scale vaccination drives, our syringes provide the tools needed to deliver optimal patient care. With our commitment to quality and innovation, we strive to support the medical community in their mission to save lives and improve health outcomes.</p><p>Choose our surgical and vaccination syringes for a blend of precision, safety, and comfort. Experience the difference that meticulous design and superior craftsmanship can make in your medical practice. Trust in our syringes to deliver the accuracy and reliability that healthcare demands.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 12, 436, 6.00, 2.82, 53.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'MEDI18', 0, 'in_stock', 'Precision Injection Solutions', 'Discover our advanced surgical and vaccination syringes, designed for precise, safe, and efficient medical procedures. Crafted with high-quality materials, these syringes ensure accurate dosing and patient comfort.', 1729, 1729, NULL, 'our order is likely to reach you within 6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'precision-injection-solutions', 1, 17, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-21 03:37:21', '2024-05-21 03:37:21'),
