ant, as it ensures consistent dosing and effectiveness. By making the process of rolling pre-rolls simpler and more efficient, the Lanneve Roll Master enhances the overall cannabis consumption experience, catering to both recreational and therapeutic needs.', 1896, 1896, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 8-10 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'lanneve-roll-master', 1, 22, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 66, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-24 00:51:35', '2024-05-24 00:51:35');
