ts. Whether used in residential settings where cannabis cultivation is restricted or in commercial environments where live plants may not be suitable, artificial plants provide a safe and hassle-free alternative. Their artificial nature eliminates concerns about allergies, pests, or seasonal changes, providing a consistent and reliable decorative accent year-round. Furthermore, they offer peace of mind for pet owners, as there is no risk of pets ingesting harmful plant material or toxins.\n\nIn addition to their decorative function, artificial marijuana plants serve as conversation starters and statement pieces, inviting curiosity and sparking discussions about cannabis culture, legalization, and botanical aesthetics. They can be used to create thematic displays at events, parties, or cannabis-themed businesses, adding an element of whimsy and intrigue. Whether displayed alone as a focal point or integrated into larger design schemes, artificial marijuana plants offer a unique and captivating way to celebrate the beauty and allure of the cannabis plant in a safe, sustainable, and aesthetically pleasing manner.', 1911, 1911, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 6-9 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'artificial-marijauna-plant', 1, 22, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 64, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-24 01:17:45', '2024-05-24 01:17:45'),
(335, 'Pink Yellow Lemonade', 'Pink Yellow Lemonade is a unique twist on traditional lemonade, blending the tangy flavors of lemon with the sweetness of strawberries and pineapple. Its vibrant pink-yellow hue and refreshing taste make it a delightful and visually appealing beverage choice for warm weather gatherings. Perfect for quenching thirst and adding a splash of color to any occasion.', '<p>Pink Yellow Lemonade is a delightful fusion of citrus flavors, blending the tartness of lemons with the sweetness of both pink and yellow citrus fruits. This refreshing beverage offers a symphony of taste sensations, with the tangy notes of lemon complemented by the subtle sweetness of pink grapefruit and the bright, sunny flavors of yellow lemons. The combination of these vibrant citrus fruits creates a harmonious balance of acidity and sweetness, resulting in a refreshing and thirst-quenching drink that is perfect for sipping on hot summer days.</p><p>Crafting Pink Yellow Lemonade involves juicing a combination of fresh lemons, pink grapefruits, and yellow lemons, then mixing the juices with water and a sweetener such as sugar or honey to taste. The result is a visually stunning beverage with a striking pink-yellow hue, evoking images of sunny days and tropical getaways. Garnishing with slices of fresh citrus fruits or sprigs of mint adds a decorative touch and enhances the drink\'s aroma and flavor.</p><p>Pink Yellow Lemonade is not only a delicious thirst quencher but also a versatile beverage that can be customized to suit individual preferences. For those who prefer a sweeter drink, additional sugar or honey can be added, while those who enjoy a more tart flavor can adjust the ratio of lemon juice to other citrus juices accordingly. Whether enjoyed as a standalone refreshment or used as a mixer in cocktails or mocktails, Pink Yellow Lemonade offers a burst of citrusy goodness that is sure to brighten any occasion.</p>', 'simple', '2 Pieces', 200, 100, 26.00, 20.80, 20.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'MAR08', 0, 'in_stock', 'Pink Yellow Lemonade', 'Pink Yellow Lemonade is a unique and vibrant twist on the classic lemonade recipe, offering a tantalizing blend of tartness and sweetness. This refreshing beverage combines the zesty flavor of lemons with the distinct tastes of both pink grapefruit and yellow lemons, resulting in a harmonious fusion of citrusy goodness. The tartness of the lemons provides a refreshing acidity, while the sweetness of the pink grapefruit and yellow lemons adds depth and complexity to the flavor profile, creating a drink that is both refreshing and satisfying.\n\nTo make Pink Yellow Lemonade, fresh lemons, pink grapefruits, and yellow lemons are juiced to extract their flavorful essence. The juices are then combined with water and a sweetener of choice, such as sugar, honey, or agave syrup, to achieve the perfect balance of tartness and sweetness. The mixture is stirred until the sweetener is fully dissolved, resulting in a refreshing and thirst-quenching beverage that is bursting with citrus flavor. For an extra touch of elegance and visual appeal, garnish the Pink Yellow Lemonade with slices of fresh citrus fruits or a sprig of mint before serving.\n\nPink Yellow Lemonade is not only delicious but also incredibly versatile, making it suitable for a wide range of occasions. Whether enjoyed on a hot summer day as a refreshing thirst quencher or served at a backyard barbecue or picnic, this vibrant beverage is sure to be a hit with guests of all ages. Additionally, Pink Yellow Lemonade can be easily transformed into a cocktail by adding a splash of vodka or gin, or kept alcohol-free for a family-friendly option. With its delightful blend of citrus flavors and eye-catching appearance, Pink Yellow Lemonade is a refreshing and irresistible drink that is perfect for any celebration or gathering.', 1916, 1916, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 4-6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1