(341, 'Cannibis Tincture Oil', 'Cannabis tincture oil is a concentrated liquid extract of cannabinoids, typically THC or CBD, infused in alcohol or glycerin. It offers a discreet and versatile method of consumption, allowing for precise dosing and rapid absorption when administered sublingually. Cannabis tincture oil is commonly used for medicinal purposes, providing relief from pain, inflammation, anxiety, and other ailments.', '<p>Cannabis tincture oil is a potent and versatile form of cannabis extract, consisting of cannabinoids, such as THC or CBD, dissolved in alcohol or glycerin. This concentrated liquid offers a discreet and convenient method of consumption, with the ability to be administered sublingually for rapid absorption into the bloodstream. Cannabis tincture oil is often preferred by medical cannabis patients for its precise dosing capabilities, allowing for accurate titration of dosage to suit individual needs and preferences.</p><p>One of the primary benefits of cannabis tincture oil is its versatility in application. It can be easily added to food or beverages for ingestion or applied topically to the skin for localized relief from pain, inflammation, or skin conditions. Additionally, its sublingual administration provides a quick and efficient way to experience the effects of cannabis, making it an ideal option for those seeking fast-acting relief from symptoms without the need for inhalation.</p><p>Moreover, cannabis tincture oil offers a discreet and odorless alternative to smoking or vaping cannabis, making it suitable for use in various settings. Its compact and portable nature allows for on-the-go dosing without drawing attention, making it an appealing option for individuals looking to maintain discretion while managing their symptoms. With its precise dosing, rapid onset of effects, and versatile application methods, cannabis tincture oil remains a popular choice among medical cannabis patients and wellness enthusiasts seeking the therapeutic benefits of cannabinoids in a convenient and accessible form.</p>', 'simple', '1 item', 500, 50, 20.00, 18.40, 8.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'MAR14', 0, 'in_stock', 'Cannibis Tincture Oil', 'Cannabis tincture oil stands as a concentrated and versatile extract derived from cannabis plants, typically containing high levels of cannabinoids such as THC (tetrahydrocannabinol) or CBD (cannabidiol). This liquid extract is carefully infused into alcohol or glycerin, resulting in a potent solution that offers a range of therapeutic benefits. One of the key advantages of cannabis tincture oil is its flexibility in dosing, allowing users to easily adjust their intake based on individual tolerance levels and desired effects. This precise control over dosage makes it an ideal choice for medical cannabis patients seeking tailored relief from various symptoms, including pain, anxiety, inflammation, and more.\n\nIn addition to its customizable dosing, cannabis tincture oil offers multiple methods of administration to suit different preferences and needs. When taken sublingually (under the tongue), the tincture is rapidly absorbed into the bloodstream, providing quick relief within minutes. Alternatively, it can be added to food or beverages for ingestion, offering a discreet and convenient way to incorporate cannabis into daily routines. Furthermore, cannabis tincture oil can be applied topically to the skin, offering localized relief from pain, soreness, and skin conditions when absorbed through the skin\'s surface.\n\nBeyond its therapeutic applications, cannabis tincture oil offers a discreet and odorless alternative to smoking or vaping cannabis, making it suitable for use in various social and professional settings. Its compact and portable nature allows for discreet dosing on-the-go, providing users with a convenient way to manage their symptoms without drawing unwanted attention. With its precise dosing, rapid onset of effects, and versatile 