ersatile accessory for any occasion. Whether paired with a tailored suit or casual attire, this watch adds a touch of refinement to any ensemble, elevating the wearer\'s overall look with its timeless elegance and modern flair.', 2192, 2189, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 4-6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'tech-classic-watch', 1, 11, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 33, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 01:22:03', '2024-06-22 00:56:30'),
(390, 'Titan Pro SmartWatch', 'The Titan Smart Pro is a stylish and versatile unisex smartwatch with a sleek round design and a durable aluminum body. It offers a variety of features to keep you connected and on track, including fitness tracking, health monitoring, and smartphone notifications. With up to 14 days of battery life, you can wear it all day and night without worry.', '<p><span style=\"color:rgb(31, 31, 31);\">The Titan Smart 3 is a smartwatch that seamlessly blends style and functionality. Featuring a large, 1.96-inch AMOLED display with a sharp 410 x 502 pixel resolution, it offers stunning visuals and a clear view of your notifications, messages, and fitness data. The sleek design boasts a comfortable fit and comes in various colors to match your personal style.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(31, 31, 31);\">This smartwatch goes beyond aesthetics, transforming into your ultimate wellness companion. It boasts an impressive 110+ sports modes, allowing you to track everything from your daily walks to intense gym sessions. Built-in GPS precisely maps your runs or bike rides, while the auto stress monitor helps you stay mindful throughout the day.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:rgb(31, 31, 31);\">Staying connected is effortless with the Titan Smart 3. Thanks to SingleSync BT Calling, you can make and receive calls directly from your wrist. Plus, you can receive notifications, respond with quick replies, and even access an AI voice assistant for added convenience. With a long-lasting battery life of up to 7 days and a range of customizable watch faces, the Titan Smart 3 is the perfect accessory for anyone seeking a feature-packed smartwatch with a touch of sophistication.</span></p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 300, 30, 19.00, 17.10, 10.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'WATC23', 0, 'in_stock', 'Titan Pro SmartWatch', 'The Titan Pro SmartWatch 4 is the epitome of sophistication and functionality in wearable technology. With its sleek