(392, 'Steel Sovereign', 'Command your kingdom, conquer your rivals, and forge your legacy in this immersive strategy game where power is the ultimate currency.', '<p>Steel Sovereign places you in the role of a powerful ruler commanding a vast kingdom. Set in a richly detailed fantasy world, this strategy game challenges you to build, expand, and conquer as you vie for dominance against rival factions. With intricate diplomacy, cunning tactics, and strategic resource management, you must navigate the complexities of politics and warfare to secure your place as the undisputed sovereign.</p><p>Forge alliances, negotiate treaties, or wage warâ€”it\'s all within your grasp as you shape the destiny of your realm. From constructing mighty fortresses to leading armies into battle, every decision you make will influence the course of history. Whether you choose to rule with an iron fist or a velvet glove, your choices will determine the fate of your people and the legacy you leave behind.</p><p>But beware, for challenges and adversaries lurk around every corner, eager to thwart your ambitions and claim your throne for themselves. Only by mastering the art of strategy and demonstrating unwavering resolve can you emerge victorious in the cutthroat world of Steel Sovereign. Will you rise to become the undisputed ruler, or will you fall to the machinations of your enemies? The fate of your kingdom hangs in the balance.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 100, 25, 25.00, 21.25, 15.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM01', 0, 'in_stock', 'Steel Sovereign', 'In the epic realm of Steel Sovereign, you ascend as a formidable ruler, tasked with navigating the intricacies of politics, warfare, and diplomacy. Embark on a journey to build a mighty empire from the ground up, strategizing every move to ensure its prosperity and dominance. From constructing grand cities to training powerful armies, your decisions shape the destiny of your realm, defining the legacy you leave behind.\n\nHarness the strength of alliances or wield the might of your armies as you engage in intense battles against rival factions. With a dynamic combat system that emphasizes strategy and tactics, every skirmish is a test of your leadership and cunning. As you expand your influence, you\'ll encounter formidable foes, cunning rivals, and unforeseen challenges that will put your skills to the ultimate test.\n\nBut true sovereignty extends beyond the battlefield, requiring shrewd diplomacy and astute governance. Navigate delicate political landscapes, forge strategic alliances, and outmaneuver rival factions to solidify your grip on power. With every decision shaping the course of history, the fate of your kingdom rests in your hands as you strive to become the undisputed Steel Sovereign.\n\nSteel Sovereign offers a rich and immersive gaming experience, blending strategic depth with captivating storytelling and stunning visuals. Whether you seek to rule with benevolence or with an iron fist, the fate of your kingdom lies in your ability to lead, conquer, and endure in the ever-changing landscape of power and ambition.', 2204, 2204, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 4-6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'steel-sovereign', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 78, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 01:59:39', '2024-05-30 01:59:39'),
