, 19.80, 10.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM02', 0, 'in_stock', 'Solstice Quest', 'In the realm of Solstice Quest, players are thrust into a mesmerizing world where the sun holds sway over all creation. This captivating RPG adventure unfolds against the backdrop of a celestial event known as the Solstice, a time of profound magic and untold mysteries. As the chosen hero, players embark on an epic quest to unlock the secrets of this ancient phenomenon and restore balance to a world in turmoil.\n\nJourney across breathtaking landscapes, from verdant forests and shimmering lakes to treacherous mountains and ethereal plains. Along the way, encounter a myriad of fantastical creatures, from noble elves and enigmatic dragons to mischievous faeries and malevolent spirits. Each encounter presents new challenges and opportunities, shaping the player\'s path and forging alliances that may prove crucial in the battles to come.\n\nMaster the art of magic and combat as you confront powerful foes and unravel the mysteries of the Solstice. Customize your character with a diverse array of skills, abilities, and equipment, allowing for endless possibilities in how you approach each challenge. From wielding elemental spells to mastering swordplay, your choices will shape your destiny and determine the fate of the world.\n\nImmerse yourself in an epic tale of adventure, discovery, and redemption, brought to life through stunning visuals, captivating storytelling, and immersive gameplay. With its richly detailed world, dynamic characters, and deep lore waiting to be uncovered, Solstice Quest offers an unforgettable gaming experience that will leave players spellbound from start to finish. Are you ready to embark on the ultimate quest and become a legend of the Solstice?', 2209, 2209, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 3-5 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'solstice-quest', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 76, NULL, '