, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM03', 0, 'in_stock', 'Steven Fields', 'Welcome to Steven Fields, a vast and enchanting world brimming with adventure, mystery, and untold treasures waiting to be discovered. As a courageous explorer, you\'ll embark on an epic journey across diverse landscapes, from lush forests and serene meadows to rugged mountains and sun-drenched deserts. Every corner of this immersive open-world game is teeming with life and possibility, inviting you to chart your own course and write your own legend.\n\nIn Steven Fields, the power to shape your destiny lies in your hands. Will you become a daring treasure hunter, scouring ancient ruins for relics of forgotten civilizations? Or perhaps you\'ll embrace the call of the wild, forging alliances with majestic creatures and uncovering the secrets of the natural world. With each decision you make and every path you choose, the fate of Steven Fields is yours to determine.\n\nBut the journey won\'t be easy. Along the way, you\'ll face formidable challenges and daunting adversaries that test your skills and resolve. From cunning bandits and fearsome beasts to ancient guardians and otherworldly beings, danger lurks at every turn. Only by honing your abilities, gathering allies, and mastering the art of strategy can you hope to overcome the obstacles that stand between you and your destiny.\n\nImmerse yourself in a richly detailed world brought to life by stunning visuals, dynamic gameplay, and a captivating soundtrack. Whether you\'re embarking on epic quests, engaging in thrilling battles, or simply taking in the breathtaking scenery, Steven Fields offers an unforgettable gaming experience that will leave you yearning for adventure long after the journey ends. So grab your sword, prepare your spells, and set forth into the wondrous realm of Steven Fieldsâ€”it\'s time to write your own story.', 2214, 2214, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 3-5 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1