he game\'s dynamic environments and atmospheric sound design create a world that feels alive and responsive to your actions. As you delve deeper into Echo Trails, you\'ll find yourself drawn into a captivating adventure where every echo tells a story, and every step brings you closer to uncovering the secrets of this mystical land. Prepare to embark on a journey that will challenge your senses, ignite your imagination, and leave an indelible mark on your gaming experience.', 2219, 2219, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 3-5 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'echo-trails', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 78, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 02:26:59', '2024-05-30 02:26:59'),
(396, 'Shadow Legacy', 'Step into the shadows and embrace your destiny as a master assassin in this gripping action-adventure game. Uncover hidden secrets, execute precise stealth maneuvers, and unravel a deep narrative steeped in intrigue and betrayal. Your legacy begins in the shadowsâ€”will you rise to become a legend.', '<p>In Shadow Legacy, players are thrust into a dark and intricate world where the line between hero and villain is blurred. As a master assassin, you must navigate a complex web of political intrigue, ancient secrets, and personal vendettas. Set against the backdrop of a richly detailed, historically inspired landscape, every mission requires cunning, precision, and a mastery of stealth. The game\'s atmospheric environments and immersive storytelling draw you into a narrative where your choices shape your destiny and the fate of those around you.</p><p>Your journey in Shadow Legacy begins with intense training and the acquisition of specialized skills. From scaling towering walls to blending into crowds, your abilities evolve as you uncover ancient artifacts and unlock powerful upgrades. The game emphasizes strategic thinking and adaptability, allowing you to approach each mission with multiple tactics. Whether you prefer silent takedowns, creating diversions, or using the environment to your advantage, the freedom to choose your path makes each playthrough unique.</p><p>The heart of Shadow Legacy lies in its rich, character-driven story. As you delve deeper into the game\'s lore, you\'ll encounter a diverse cast of allies and adversaries, each with their own motivations and secrets. Form alliances, make pivotal decisions, and face the consequences of your actions in a world where betrayal lurks at every corner. With its breathtaking visuals, dynamic gameplay, and compelling narrative, Shadow Legacy offers an unforgettable experience that challenges your skills and immerses you in the shadows of history.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 200, 50, 25.00, 22.00, 12.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM05', 0, 'in_stock', 'Shadow Legacy', 'In Shadow Legacy, players are thrust into a dark and intricate world where the line between hero and villain is blurred. As a master assassin, you must navigate a complex web of political intrigue, ancient secrets, and personal vendettas. Set against the backdrop of a richly detailed, historically inspired landscape, every mission requires cunning, precision, and a mastery of stealth. The game\'s atmospheric environments and immersive storytelling draw you into a narrative where your choices shape your destiny and the fate of those around you.\n\nYour journey in Shadow Legacy begins with intense training and the acquisition of specialized skills. From scaling towering walls to blending into crowds, your abilities evolve as you uncover ancient artifacts and unlock powerful upgrades. The game emphasizes strategic thinking and adaptability, allowing you to approach each mission with multiple tactics. Whether you prefer silent takedowns, creating diversions, or using the environment to your advantage, the freedom to choose your path makes each playthrough unique. The dynamic weather and day-night cycle further enhance the gameplay, adding layers of complexity to your stealth operations.\n\nThe heart of Shadow Legacy lies in its rich, character-driven story. As you delve deeper into the game\'s lore, you\'ll encounter a diverse cast of allies and adversaries, each with their own motivations and secrets. Form alliances, make pivotal decisions, and face the consequences of your actions in a world where betrayal lurks at every corner. Intricate dialogue options and branching storylines ensure that your journey is deeply personal and reflective of your choices. Each character you meet and each alliance you forge can alter the course of the narrative, making every decision critical.\n\nWith its breathtaking visuals, dynamic gameplay, and compelling narrative, Shadow Legacy offers an unforgettable experience that challenges your skills and immerses you in the shadows of history. The meticulously crafted environments, from bustling cities to hidden temples, provide a rich playground for your assassin\'s exploits. The hauntingly beautiful soundtrack complements the intense action, drawing you deeper into the world of espionage and intrigue. Prepare to step into the shadows, embrace your legacy, and carve your own path in a game where every move can change the course of history.', 2224, 2224, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 3-5 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'shadow-legacy', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 77, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 02:40:28', '2024-05-30 02:40:28'),
(397, 'Metro Exodus', '**Metro Exodus** is a first-person shooter with survival horror elements set in a post-apocalyptic Russia. Players embark on a journey across the country with a group of survivors, facing various dangers, including mutated creatures and hostile humans. The game features a mix of open-world exploration and linear levels, emphasizing immersive environments, narrative depth, and resource management.', '<p>**Metro Exodus** is a first-person shooter developed by 4A Games, set in a post-apocalyptic Russia devastated by nuclear war. The game follows Artyom and his companions as they embark on a perilous journey across the country aboard the Aurora, a heavily modified steam locomotive. The storyline picks up from the events of **Metro: Last Light**, with Artyom seeking a new life beyond the irradiated ruins of Moscow. The game combines elements of survival horror, stealth, and open-world exploration, offering players a rich, immersive experience.</p><p>The game\'s environments range from the harsh, frozen wastelands of the Volga River to the arid deserts of the Caspian Sea, each meticulously crafted to provide a unique atmosphere and challenge. The dynamic weather system and day-night cycles add realism and depth, influencing both the behavior of enemies and the strategies players must employ. Scavenging for resources, crafting essential items, and managing limited supplies are crucial for survival. Metro Exodus places a strong emphasis on narrative, with deep, character-driven storytelling that explores themes of hope, resilience, and the human spirit.</p><p>Combat in **Metro Exodus** is intense and varied, combining traditional first-person shooting with stealth elements. Players can customize their weapons using a detailed modification system, tailoring their loadout to suit different situations. Encounters with mutated creatures and hostile humans require strategic thinking and adaptability. The game\'s audio design and visuals work together to create a tense, immersive atmosphere, keeping players on edge as they navigate the dangerous world. Overall, **Metro Exodus** is a compelling blend of action, exploration, and storytelling, offering a unique and memorable post-apocalyptic adventure.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 200, 50, 24.00, 21.60, 10.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM06', 0, 'in_stock', 'Metro Exodus', '**Metro Exodus** is a first-person shooter developed by 4A Games, continuing the story of Artyom in a post-apocalyptic Russia ravaged by nuclear war. Following the events of **Metro: Last Light**, Artyom and his fellow survivors embark on a quest to find a new safe haven beyond the irradiated ruins of Moscow. Traveling aboard the Aurora, a heavily modified steam locomotive, they venture across vast and varied landscapes in search of a new beginning. The game blends elements of survival horror, stealth, and open-world exploration, delivering a rich and immersive experience that stands out in the series.\n\nThe environments in **Metro Exodus** are diverse and intricately designed, ranging from the snow-covered wastelands of the Volga River to the scorching deserts of the Caspian Sea. Each region presents unique challenges and atmospheres, enhanced by a dynamic weather system and day-night cycles that affect both gameplay and enemy behavior. Players must adapt to these changing conditions, using stealth to avoid detection or engaging in combat when necessary. Resource management is critical, as players scavenge for supplies, craft essential items, and maintain their weapons to survive the harsh and unforgiving world.\n\nNarrative depth is a hallmark of **Metro Exodus**, with a strong emphasis on character development and storytelling. The game explores themes of hope, resilience, and the human spirit as Artyom and his companions face numerous trials and tribulations on their journey. The characters\' interactions and personal stories add emotional weight to the game, making the player\'s decisions and actions feel meaningful. This narrative richness is complemented by the game\'s stunning visuals and atmospheric audio design, which together create an immersive and tension-filled experience.\n\nCombat in **Metro Exodus** is varied and intense, combining traditional first-person shooting mechanics with stealth elements. Players can customize their weapons with a detailed modification system, allowing for a tailored approach to different combat scenarios. Encounters with mutated creatures and hostile human factions require strategic thinking and adaptability, as players must balance aggression with caution. The game\'s open-world segments encourage exploration, rewarding players with hidden resources and story elements that enrich the overall experience. **Metro Exodus** successfully merges action, exploration, and storytelling, offering a unique and compelling post-apocalyptic adventure that captivates players from start to finish.', 2229, 2229, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 4-6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'metro-exodus', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 78, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 19:49:02', '2024-05-30 19:49:02'),
(398, 'Aliens Colonial Marine', '**Aliens: Colonial Marines** is a first-person shooter set in the iconic Aliens universe, where players control a squad of Colonial Marines battling xenomorphs and Weyland-Yutani mercenaries. The game features cooperative gameplay, allowing players to team up and tackle missions together. It emphasizes atmospheric environments, authentic weaponry, and the intense, survival-based combat fans expect from the franchise.', '<p>**Aliens: Colonial Marines** is a first-person shooter developed by Gearbox Software, set in the iconic universe of the Alien franchise. Players take on the role of a Colonial Marine, part of a squad sent to investigate the disappearance of the USS Sulaco and uncover the mysteries surrounding the abandoned Hadley\'s Hope colony on LV-426. The game strives to capture the intense and atmospheric horror of the films, immersing players in dark, claustrophobic environments teeming with deadly xenomorphs.</p><p>The gameplay of **Aliens: Colonial Marines** emphasizes cooperative multiplayer, allowing up to four players to team up and tackle missions together. Players can choose from a variety of marine classes, each with unique abilities and weapon loadouts, fostering a team-based approach to combat. The arsenal includes iconic weapons from the films, such as pulse rifles and flamethrowers, which players can customize and upgrade. The game also features a competitive multiplayer mode where players can assume the role of either marines or xenomorphs, adding variety and replayability to the experience.</p><p>Visually and thematically, **Aliens: Colonial Marines** aims to stay true to the aesthetic of the films, with meticulously recreated sets and sound design that evoke the same tension and dread. Despite its ambition, the game received mixed reviews upon release, with criticism directed at its graphics, AI behavior, and overall polish. However, it remains a noteworthy title for fans of the Alien franchise, offering a chance to engage directly with the lore and settings of one of the most influential sci-fi horror series in cinema.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 100, 50, 20.00, 17.20, 14.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM07', 0, 'in_stock', 'Aliens Colonial Marine', '**Aliens: Colonial Marines** is a first-person shooter developed by Gearbox Software and published by Sega. Set in the storied universe of the Alien franchise, the game places players in the role of a Colonial Marine named Cpl. Christopher Winter. The narrative picks up after the events of the film *Aliens* and follows a squad of marines dispatched to the USS Sulaco and the devastated Hadley\'s Hope colony on LV-426. Their mission is to investigate the fate of their comrades and uncover the sinister activities of the Weyland-Yutani Corporation. The game seeks to replicate the tense, atmospheric horror of the films, offering an immersive experience filled with dark, foreboding environments and relentless xenomorph threats.\n\nThe core gameplay of **Aliens: Colonial Marines** emphasizes squad-based combat and cooperative multiplayer. Up to four players can team up to take on the campaign, each choosing from different marine classes with unique abilities and weapon loadouts, promoting a strategic, team-oriented approach. The game\'s arsenal features iconic weapons from the Alien franchise, such as the pulse rifle, flamethrower, and smart gun, which players can customize and upgrade to suit their playstyle. In addition to the cooperative campaign, the game offers competitive multiplayer modes where players can engage in battles as either marines or xenomorphs, adding variety and replayability.\n\nVisually, **Aliens: Colonial Marines** aims to faithfully recreate the look and feel of the Alien universe, drawing heavily from the aesthetic of James Cameron\'s *Aliens*. The environments are meticulously detailed, from the eerie corridors of the Sulaco to the desolate remains of Hadley\'s Hope. The sound design plays a crucial role in building tension, using the familiar sounds of motion trackers, alien screeches, and the pulse rifle\'s distinct firing noise to keep players on edge. The game strives to create an atmosphere of constant dread, reflecting the high stakes and perilous nature of the marines\' mission.\n\nDespite its ambitious premise and deep connection to the beloved franchise, **Aliens: Colonial Marines** received mixed reviews upon its release. Critics cited issues with the game\'s graphics, AI behavior, and overall execution, which fell short of the high expectations set by its source material. Technical shortcomings and a lack of polish were often highlighted as detracting from the immersion and enjoyment. However, for fans of the Alien series, the game still offers a chance to engage directly with the lore and settings of a cinematic classic, providing moments of genuine tension and excitement within the familiar, haunting world of xenomorphs and space marines.', 2234, 2234, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 4-6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'aliens-colonial-marine', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 78, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 19:59:38', '2024-05-30 19:59:38'),
(399, 'BioShock Series', 'The **BioShock** series is a collection of first-person shooter games known for their immersive storytelling, atmospheric worlds, and unique art direction. Set in dystopian environments, players navigate through rich narratives filled with moral choices and philosophical themes. From the depths of Rapture to the heights of Columbia, each game offers a captivating journey filled with mystery and intrigue.', '<p>The **BioShock** series is a celebrated collection of first-person shooter games renowned for their immersive storytelling, atmospheric worlds, and unique art direction. Developed by Irrational Games (now known as Ghost Story Games) and later by 2K Marin and 2K Australia, the series has captivated players with its deep narratives and thought-provoking themes.</p><p>Set in dystopian environments such as the underwater city of Rapture and the floating city of Columbia, each game in the series offers a distinct and unforgettable experience. Players are thrust into morally ambiguous scenarios, confronting philosophical dilemmas and making consequential choices that shape the outcome of the narrative. From battling genetically-enhanced splicers in the decaying halls of Rapture to confronting zealous extremists in the sky-high streets of Columbia, the **BioShock** series challenges players to explore complex worlds filled with intrigue and danger.</p><p>At the heart of the **BioShock** experience is its narrative depth and thematic richness. Each game delves into themes of objectivism, free will, and the consequences of unchecked ambition, inviting players to contemplate the nature of power and morality. Coupled with its evocative art deco and steampunk-inspired aesthetics, the series creates a hauntingly beautiful backdrop for its gripping tales of hubris and downfall.</p><p>From its groundbreaking debut in 2007 to its latest installment, the **BioShock** series continues to leave a lasting legacy in the gaming industry, earning critical acclaim and a dedicated fanbase. With its masterful storytelling, immersive environments, and philosophical depth, the series stands as a testament to the power of video games as a storytelling medium.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 150, 50, 20.00, 17.00, 15.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM08', 0, 'in_stock', 'BioShock Series', 'The **BioShock** series stands as a testament to the heights that narrative-driven gaming can reach, captivating players with its rich storytelling, immersive atmospheres, and thought-provoking themes. Developed by Irrational Games and later continued by 2K Marin and 2K Australia, each installment in the series presents a unique dystopian setting filled with moral ambiguity and philosophical depth.\n\nAt the core of the **BioShock** experience is its ability to immerse players in intricately crafted worlds that are as fascinating as they are disturbing. From the underwater utopia-turned-dystopia of Rapture in the original game to the sky-bound city of Columbia in **BioShock Infinite**, players are transported to environments that are teeming with life, both beautiful and grotesque. These locales serve as more than mere backdrops; they are characters in their own right, each with its own history, secrets, and dark undercurrents waiting to be uncovered.\n\nOne of the defining features of the series is its exploration of complex philosophical and ethical questions. Through its narrative arcs and character interactions, **BioShock** challenges players to confront issues of morality, free will, and the consequences of unchecked power. Whether wrestling with the ideologies of Andrew Ryan in Rapture or navigating the racial tensions of Columbia, players are invited to ponder the implications of their choices within the game world and beyond.\n\nIn addition to its narrative depth, the **BioShock** series is also known for its innovative gameplay mechanics and memorable moments. From the iconic introduction to Rapture in the original game to the mind-bending twists and turns of **BioShock Infinite**, each installment delivers gameplay experiences that are as engaging as they are thought-provoking. Whether engaging in intense combat with genetically modified splicers or unraveling the mysteries of quantum physics, players are kept on the edge of their seats from start to finish.', 2239, 2239, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 4-6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'bioshock-series', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 78, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 20:11:25', '2024-05-30 20:11:25'),
(400, 'Apex Legends Game', '\"Apex Legends\" is a free-to-play battle royale game renowned for its fast-paced action, diverse cast of characters (Legends), and strategic team-based gameplay. Players form squads of three and compete against other teams to be the last squad standing on the ever-shrinking map, utilizing unique abilities and teamwork to secure victory. With frequent updates, dynamic gameplay, and a vibrant community, it continues to captivate players worldwide.', '<p>\"Apex Legends\" is a free-to-play battle royale game developed by Respawn Entertainment, set in the Titanfall universe. In this fast-paced multiplayer shooter, players form squads of three Legends, each with their own unique abilities, and compete against other teams on a sprawling map. Combining elements of tactical team play, character-based strategy, and skillful gunplay, \"Apex Legends\" offers an exhilarating experience that rewards both individual skill and teamwork.</p><p>The game\'s diverse roster of Legends includes characters with varying abilities, ranging from offensive powerhouses to support specialists and tactical geniuses. Players must strategically choose their Legends and coordinate with their teammates to leverage their abilities effectively, whether it\'s deploying defensive barriers, healing teammates, or launching devastating attacks. The dynamic interplay between Legend abilities adds depth and complexity to each match, creating opportunities for creative strategies and clutch plays.</p><p>Set in the vibrant Outlands, \"Apex Legends\" features a dynamic map filled with diverse landscapes, from urban environments to natural terrain and industrial facilities. As the match progresses, a shrinking play area forces players into increasingly intense engagements, leading to thrilling showdowns in the final circles. With regular updates, seasonal events, and a passionate community, \"Apex Legends\" continues to evolve, offering endless excitement and challenges for players seeking the ultimate battle royale experience.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 200, 40, 24.00, 20.40, 15.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM09', 0, 'in_stock', 'Apex Legends Game', '\"Apex Legends\" stands as a pinnacle of the battle royale genre, offering a dynamic and adrenaline-fueled gaming experience unlike any other. Developed by Respawn Entertainment, the game plunges players into the heart of the Frontier, a dangerous and vibrant world filled with competing factions and powerful technology. In this free-to-play title, players assume the roles of Legends, skilled fighters with unique abilities and backstories, each adding a layer of depth and strategy to the fast-paced matches.\n\nThe core gameplay of \"Apex Legends\" revolves around teams of three competing against each other in a high-stakes battle for survival. From the moment players drop onto the map, tension builds as they scavenge for weapons, equipment, and resources while dodging enemy fire and navigating treacherous terrain. With the looming threat of a deadly ring that steadily closes in, matches escalate into intense confrontations, requiring cunning tactics, precise shooting, and coordinated teamwork to emerge victorious.\n\nWhat sets \"Apex Legends\" apart is its emphasis on squad-based gameplay and character-driven mechanics. Each Legend brings a unique set of abilities to the table, ranging from offensive powers to defensive utilities and support functions. Crafting the perfect team composition and synergizing abilities with teammates can turn the tide of battle, creating thrilling moments of cooperation and heroism. Whether deploying defensive shields as Gibraltar, tracking enemies with Bloodhound\'s keen senses, or teleporting across the battlefield with Wraith\'s voidwalker abilities, the diverse roster of Legends offers endless opportunities for strategic play and dynamic combat.\n\nBeyond its compelling gameplay, \"Apex Legends\" boasts a richly detailed world brimming with lore and personality. From the towering skyscrapers of Kings Canyon to the lush forests of World\'s Edge, each location tells a story of the Frontier\'s tumultuous past and uncertain future. With regular updates, seasonal events, and a dedicated community, \"Apex Legends\" continues to evolve, promising exciting new content and experiences for players to enjoy as they embark on their journey to become champions of the arena.', 2244, 2244, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 3-5 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'apex-legends-game', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 78, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 20:17:28', '2024-05-30 20:17:28'),
(401, 'Groundhog Day', 'Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son\" is a virtual reality adventure game inspired by the classic film. Players step into the shoes of Phil Connors Jr. as he relives the same day in Punxsutawney, Pennsylvania, attempting to break the time loop. With interactive storytelling and engaging puzzles, it offers a fresh take on the beloved concept', '<p>\"Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son\" is a virtual reality adventure game that serves as a sequel to the iconic film \"Groundhog Day.\" Players assume the role of Phil Connors Jr., the son of the original protagonist, Phil Connors, as he finds himself trapped in a time loop, reliving the same day over and over again in Punxsutawney, Pennsylvania. As Phil Jr., players must navigate through various scenarios, interact with characters, and solve puzzles to break free from the temporal anomaly.</p><p>The game captures the essence of the beloved film while offering a fresh and immersive experience in virtual reality. Players explore familiar locations from the movie, including Gobbler\'s Knob and the town square, as they uncover new storylines and encounter memorable characters. Each day presents opportunities to make different choices and explore alternative paths, leading to multiple endings and branching narratives.</p><p>With its engaging storytelling, interactive gameplay, and innovative use of virtual reality technology, \"Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son\" offers players a chance to revisit the world of \"Groundhog Day\" in a whole new way. Whether they\'re fans of the original film or newcomers to the franchise, players will find themselves drawn into a captivating adventure filled with humor, heart, and the timeless message of redemption and self-discovery.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 100, 45, 25.00, 22.00, 12.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM10', 0, 'in_stock', 'Groundhog Day', '\"Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son\" is a virtual reality adventure game that invites players to step into the shoes of Phil Connors Jr., the son of the original film\'s protagonist, as he navigates the same time loop that trapped his father. Set in the quaint town of Punxsutawney, Pennsylvania, players relive the events of February 2nd over and over again, exploring the intricacies of the time loop and uncovering the mysteries of their family\'s past.\n\nAs Phil Jr., players are tasked with unraveling the secrets of the time loop by interacting with the town\'s inhabitants, solving puzzles, and making meaningful choices that shape the outcome of the story. With each repeated day, players gain new insights, forge connections with characters, and discover hidden pathways that lead to different endings. The game\'s branching narrative ensures that every decision matters, offering a dynamic and immersive gameplay experience.\n\nDrawing inspiration from the beloved film, \"Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son\" captures the essence of its source material while expanding upon its universe in exciting new ways. Through its engaging storytelling, witty dialogue, and charming characters, the game immerses players in the quirky world of Punxsutawney and invites them to explore its secrets at their own pace. Whether they\'re solving puzzles, engaging in heartfelt conversations, or simply soaking in the atmosphere, players will find themselves captivated by the timeless charm of the \"Groundhog Day\" experience.\n\nWith its innovative use of virtual reality technology, \"Groundhog Day: Like Father Like Son\" offers players a truly immersive and interactive journey through the iconic time loop. Whether they\'re reliving classic moments from the film or forging their own path to freedom, players will find themselves drawn into a captivating adventure filled with humor, heart, and the promise of redemption.', 2249, 2249, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 3-5 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'groundhog-day', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 76, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 20:26:27', '2024-05-30 20:26:27');
