(410, 'Elder Scroll legends', '\"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" is a strategic card game set in the richly detailed universe of Tamriel. Players build powerful decks, summon legendary creatures, and unleash potent spells as they compete in tactical battles against foes from across the realm. With deep strategic depth, immersive lore, and thrilling multiplayer gameplay, \"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" offers an epic card game experience for fans of the acclaimed Elder Scrolls series.', '<p>\"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" invites players to immerse themselves in the rich and diverse world of Tamriel through the medium of strategic card battles. Set within the expansive lore of The Elder Scrolls universe, players construct decks comprising iconic characters, powerful creatures, and formidable spells drawn from the depths of Tamriel\'s history. With each card representing a unique facet of the Elder Scrolls lore, players engage in tactical duels where every decision counts.</p><p>In \"Elder Scrolls: Legends,\" players embark on a journey across the varied landscapes of Tamriel, from the snow-capped peaks of Skyrim to the sprawling deserts of Hammerfell. As they progress, they encounter familiar faces and iconic locations, each steeped in the rich tapestry of Elder Scrolls lore. Through strategic deck-building and shrewd decision-making, players navigate through an ever-evolving metagame, adapting their tactics to outwit opponents and emerge victorious in the ongoing struggle for supremacy.</p><p>With its deep strategic gameplay, captivating storytelling, and stunning artwork, \"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" offers an immersive card game experience unlike any other. Whether engaging in thrilling multiplayer battles, embarking on solo adventures, or delving into epic PvE campaigns, players will find themselves drawn deeper into the world of Tamriel with every card they play. \"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" is a testament to the enduring legacy of The Elder Scrolls series, offering fans a new and exciting way to experience the wonders of Tamriel\'s vast and vibrant world.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 150, 50, 20.00, 19.40, 3.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GAM19', 0, 'in_stock', 'Elder Scroll legends', '\"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" invites players to embark on an epic journey through the rich and storied universe of Tamriel, where every card drawn represents a piece of the realm\'s captivating lore. Assembled from a vast array of iconic characters, creatures, and spells, players construct decks that reflect their strategic prowess and delve into tactical battles against foes from across the land. Whether commanding the mighty forces of Skyrim\'s Nords, channeling the arcane energies of the Mages Guild, or summoning the otherworldly Daedra, every deck in \"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" tells a unique story of conquest and triumph.\n\nWithin \"Elder Scrolls: Legends,\" players find themselves immersed in a world of boundless possibilities, where alliances are forged, betrayals are enacted, and legends are born. Traverse the diverse landscapes of Tamriel, from the rugged wilderness of Morrowind to the bustling cities of Cyrodiil, encountering iconic characters and unraveling mysteries along the way. With each victory, players earn rewards that allow them to expand their collection, unlocking new cards and abilities to further customize their decks and refine their strategies.\n\nBut the path to victory in \"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" is fraught with peril, as cunning opponents and deadly challenges test players\' mettle at every turn. Whether facing off against AI opponents in gripping solo campaigns or pitting their skills against fellow players in intense multiplayer battles, every duel is a test of skill, strategy, and nerve. With its deep strategic gameplay, immersive storytelling, and stunning visuals, \"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" offers an unparalleled card game experience that transports players deep into the heart of Tamriel\'s ever-expanding lore.\n\nAs players rise through the ranks and carve out their legend in the annals of Tamrielic history, they become part of a vibrant community of fellow adventurers, united by their love for The Elder Scrolls series. \"Elder Scrolls: Legends\" is more than just a card game; it\'s a gateway to the fantastical world of Tamriel, where heroes are forged, empires rise and fall, and the fate of the realm hangs in the balance. So gather your cards, sharpen your wits, and prepare to embark on an unforgettable journey through the realms of Elder Scrolls: Legends.\"', 2295, 2295, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 4-6 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'elder-scroll-legends', 1, 26, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 'center', 78, NULL, 'fixed', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 21:50:16', '2024-05-30 21:50:16'),
