ory weaves a tapestry of adventure, romance, and intrigue. Get ready to be transported to the past in this spellbinding anthology.', 2500, 2501, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'echoes-of-the-past', 1, 21, 1, 1, NULL, 'physical', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-06 01:07:52', '2024-06-06 01:23:18');
