t it be your guiding light. Discover the transformative power of perseverance and unlock the limitless potential that lies within. Remember, success is not determined by how many times you fall, but by how many times you choose to rise again. Don\'t quitâ€”embrace the journey, and watch as your resilience propels you towards greatness.</span></span></p>', 'simple', '1 Book', 150, 60, 5.00, 4.25, 15.00, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'BO15', NULL, 'in_stock', 'The Power of Not Giving Up', 'This compelling guide celebrates the strength found in perseverance. Learn how to navigate challenges, overcome setbacks, and embrace the journey towards success. Don\'t quitâ€”find inspiration to keep pushing forward, no matter the obstacles.', 2515, 2516, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'the-power-of-not-giving-up', 1, 21, 1, NULL, NULL, 'physical', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-06 01:07:53', '2024-06-06 01:07:53'),
