(427, 'Sunset Soft Board', 'The Sunset Soft Board surfboard offers a perfect blend of durability and performance for surfers of all skill levels. Its soft top construction ensures safety and comfort, while the sleek design enhances maneuverability on the waves. Ideal for beginners and experienced surfers alike, this board provides a stable and enjoyable ride.', '<p>The Sunset Soft Board surfboard is a versatile and user-friendly option, designed to cater to surfers of all experience levels. Its construction features a soft top deck, which not only provides a cushioned surface for added comfort but also ensures safety by minimizing the risk of injuries during falls. The durable EPS core and high-density polyethylene bottom enhance the board\'s overall resilience and performance, making it a reliable choice for various wave conditions.</p><p>One of the standout features of the Sunset Soft Board is its ease of use. The board\'s design prioritizes stability and balance, making it an excellent option for beginners who are still learning the basics of surfing. At the same time, its responsive and lightweight nature allows more experienced surfers to perform advanced maneuvers with ease. The soft fins included with the board further contribute to a safer surfing experience, reducing the likelihood of cuts or bruises.</p><p>Aesthetically, the Sunset Soft Board boasts a sleek and stylish appearance, available in a range of vibrant colors and patterns that appeal to a wide audience. Its construction is not only functional but also environmentally friendly, incorporating sustainable materials wherever possible. Whether you\'re catching your first wave or perfecting your technique, the Sunset Soft Board surfboard offers a fun, safe, and high-performing option for every surfer.</p>', 'simple', '1 Item', 1000, 20, 30.00, 26.40, 12.00, 0, NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'SUR01', 0, 'in_stock', 'Sunset Soft Board', 'The Sunset Soft Board surfboard is a top choice for surfers of all levels, combining durability, performance, and safety in one versatile package. Its design features a soft top deck, providing a cushioned surface that significantly reduces the risk of injuries during falls. This makes it an excellent option for beginners who are still mastering the basics of surfing, as well as for more experienced surfers seeking a reliable board for casual rides.\n\nConstructed with a high-density EPS core, the Sunset Soft Board offers exceptional buoyancy and stability, allowing for easy paddling and balance on the waves. The bottom of the board is made from high-density polyethylene, which enhances its overall strength and longevity, ensuring it can withstand the rigors of frequent use in various wave conditions. Additionally, the board\'s slick bottom surface reduces drag, helping surfers glide smoothly over the water.\n\nOne of the key advantages of the Sunset Soft Board is its user-friendly design. The board is equipped with soft, flexible fins that provide adequate control and maneuverability without the sharp edges that can cause injuries. This thoughtful design element makes the board not only safer for the surfer but also for others in the water. The board\'s wide, rounded shape further contributes to its stability, making it easier for surfers to catch and ride waves successfully.\n\nAesthetically, the Sunset Soft Board stands out with its vibrant colors and stylish patterns, appealing to surfers of all ages. Beyond its visual appeal, the board is also environmentally friendly, incorporating sustainable materials in its construction. Whether you\'re catching your first wave or looking to refine your surfing skills, the Sunset Soft Board surfboard offers a perfect blend of safety, performance, and style, ensuring a fun and enjoyable surfing experience for everyone.', 2576, 2576, NULL, 'Your order is likely to reach you within 3-5 days.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'sunset-soft-board', 1, 27, 1, 1, 'url', 'physical', NULL, 