(18, 'Moisture-wicking', 'moisture-wicking', 'product', 'Experience ultimate comfort with our moisture-wicking apparel, designed to keep you dry and cool during intense workouts or busy days. Engineered with advanced fabric technology, our garments efficiently pull moisture away from your skin, ensuring you stay fresh and focused, no matter the activity.', 1, 1, '2024-05-07 05:02:28', '2024-05-07 05:02:28', NULL),
