(45, 'Refreshing Scent', 'refreshing-scent', 'product', 'Indulge in the invigorating allure of our Refreshing Scent perfume. Crafted with the essence of crisp citrus notes and delicate floral undertones, it captivates with its revitalizing aroma. Perfect for every occasion, this fragrance leaves a lasting impression, enveloping you in a cloud of freshness that uplifts your senses and energizes your spirit.', 1, 1, '2024-05-17 04:43:20', '2024-05-17 04:43:20', NULL),
(46, 'Nursery Essentials', 'nursery-essentials', 'product', 'Nursery Essentials offers a curated selection of must-have baby items to create the perfect nursery. From cozy bedding sets to practical storage solutions, our collection ensures both style and functionality. Prepare for your little one\'s arrival with our range of essential nursery items, designed to make parenting easier and more enjoyable.', 1, 1, '2024-05-20 20:57:17', '2024-05-20 20:57:26', NULL),
(47, 'Baby Accessories', 'baby-accessories', 'product', 'Discover a world of comfort and style with our range of baby accessories. From cozy blankets to adorable bibs and practical diaper bags, we\'ve got everything you need to keep your little one happy and comfortable. Our products are crafted with care and designed to make parenting easier, so you can focus on creating beautiful moments with your bundle of joy.', 1, 1, '2024-05-20 20:58:06', '2024-05-20 20:58:06', NULL),
(48, 'Baby Care', 'baby-care', 'product', 'Discover our comprehensive range of baby care essentials, meticulously crafted to cater to every need of your little one. From gentle skincare products to cozy apparel and everything in between, our collection ensures tender care for your baby\'s well-being. Trust in quality, comfort, and safety with our thoughtfully curated selection.', 1, 1, '2024-05-20 20:59:00', '2024-05-20 20:59:00', NULL),
(49, 'Health Supplies', 'health-supplies', 'product', 'Explore our comprehensive range of health supplies, including vitamins, supplements, first aid kits, and more. From everyday essentials to specialized items, we\'ve got you covered for all your health and wellness needs. Stay prepared and take care of yourself with our high-quality health supplies.', 1, 1, '2024-05-21 00:40:47', '2024-05-21 00:40:47', NULL),
(50, 'Medical Supplies', 'medical-supplies', 'product', 'Browse our extensive selection of medical supplies, ranging from first aid kits to diagnostic equipment. Our products are sourced from trusted manufacturers to ensure quality and reliability. Whether you\'re a healthcare professional or a caregiver, we have everything you need to support your patients and loved ones.', 1, 1, '2024-05-21 00:41:14', '2024-05-21 00:41:14', NULL),
