(52, 'Smoothie Mix', 'smoothie-mix', 'product', 'Upgrade your mornings with delicious, nutrient-packed smoothie mixes! Made with real fruits, healthy fats, and powerful superfoods, our blends are the perfect way to start your day fueled and satisfied.', 1, 1, '2024-05-21 01:49:01', '2024-05-21 01:49:01', NULL),
