(55, 'Yoga Essentials', 'yoga-essentials', 'product', 'Discover the key tools for your yoga journey with our Yoga Essentials kit. From a non-slip mat to comfortable blocks and straps, this curated set provides everything you need to enhance your practice. Elevate your yoga experience and find balance, strength, and flexibility with ease.', 1, 1, '2024-05-21 02:21:24', '2024-05-21 02:21:24', NULL),
(56, 'Yoga Clothing', 'yoga-clothing', 'product', 'Experience comfort and style during your yoga sessions with our premium yoga clothing. Crafted from breathable fabrics, our attire ensures unrestricted movement and moisture-wicking properties for a dry and focused practice. Elevate your yoga experience with our sleek designs and embrace the harmony of mind, body, and fashion.', 1, 1, '2024-05-21 02:22:03', '2024-05-21 02:22:03', NULL),
(57, 'Yoga Props', 'yoga-props', 'product', 'Enhance your yoga practice with our premium selection of yoga props. From blocks to straps, bolster cushions to blankets, we offer everything you need to deepen stretches, improve alignment, and find comfort in your poses. Elevate your experience and achieve greater flexibility, stability, and relaxation with our durable and versatile yoga props.', 1, 1, '2024-05-21 02:22:48', '2024-05-21 02:22:48', NULL),
(58, 'Seasonal blooms', 'seasonal-blooms', 'product', 'Discover nature\'s artistry with our Seasonal Blooms collection. Each bloom is a fleeting masterpiece, embodying the essence of the changing seasons. From delicate spring blossoms to vibrant summer blooms, autumnal hues, and winter wonders, immerse yourself in the beauty of nature\'s ever-changing palette. Experience the joy of bringing the outdoors inside with our curated selection of seasonal flowers.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 00:05:50', '2024-05-23 00:05:50', NULL),
(59, 'Hand-tied bouquets', 'hand-tied-bouquets', 'product', 'Crafted with care and creativity, our hand-tied bouquets are a perfect blend of elegance and charm. Each arrangement is thoughtfully composed by skilled florists using fresh, vibrant blooms, creating a stunning gift for any occasion. Delight your loved ones with the beauty of nature\'s finest hand-picked and artfully arranged just for them.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 00:06:19', '2024-05-23 00:06:19', NULL),
(60, 'Floral design', 'floral-design', 'product', 'Elevate your space with our exquisite floral designs. Each arrangement is meticulously crafted to bring a touch of natural beauty into your home or event. From vibrant bouquets to elegant centerpieces, our floral creations promise to add a refreshing burst of color and charm to any setting.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 00:06:52', '2024-05-23 00:06:52', NULL),
(61, 'Fiction', 'fiction', 'product', 'Embark on a thrilling journey through worlds unknown with our latest fiction anthology. Dive into captivating tales crafted by master storytellers, where each page unveils new adventures and characters to enchant your imagination. Immerse yourself in the magic of storytelling with this diverse collection of fiction wonders.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 00:14:54', '2024-05-23 00:14:54', NULL),
(62, 'Non-fiction', 'non-fiction', 'product', 'Explore the fascinating world of non-fiction with our curated collection. From riveting biographies to insightful historical accounts, delve into real-life stories that inspire, educate, and entertain. Discover new perspectives, gain knowledge, and embark on intellectual journeys that will broaden your understanding of the world around you.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 00:15:18', '2024-05-23 00:15:18', NULL),
(63, 'Novella', 'novella', 'product', 'They are captivating tales of love, loss, and redemption set in the charming backdrop of a quaint European village. With rich character development and vivid storytelling, this novella promises to whisk you away on an unforgettable journey of emotions and discovery. Perfect for cozy evenings curled up with a good book.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 00:16:42', '2024-05-23 00:16:42', NULL),
(64, 'Medical marijuana', 'medical-marijuana', 'product', 'Explore the therapeutic benefits of medical marijuana. Our carefully curated selection offers relief for various ailments, from chronic pain to anxiety. Discover premium strains cultivated to deliver potent medicinal properties, ensuring a natural approach to wellness.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 23:47:17', '2024-05-23 23:47:17', NULL),
(65, 'Marijuana edibles', 'marijuana-edibles', 'product', 'Explore a deliciously discreet way to enjoy cannabis with our range of marijuana edibles. Indulge in a variety of treats infused with high-quality THC or CBD, offering a unique and enjoyable experience. Perfect for those looking for an alternative to smoking, each edible provides a precise dose for a consistent and controlled high.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 23:47:39', '2024-05-23 23:47:39', NULL),
(66, 'Marijuana concentrates', 'marijuana-concentrates', 'product', 'Explore potent marijuana concentrates for a heightened cannabis experience. Extracted from the plant\'s cannabinoids, concentrates offer intense effects in small doses. Choose from a variety of forms including shatter, wax, oil, and live resin, each boasting distinct flavors and THC levels. Elevate your consumption with these concentrated forms of marijuana.', 1, 1, '2024-05-23 23:48:07', '2024-05-23 23:48:07', NULL),
(67, 'Holiday Shopping', 'holiday-shopping', 'product', 'Get your holiday shopping done stress-free with our premium selection of marijuana products. From calming CBD-infused treats to euphoria-inducing strains, we have something for every cannabis enthusiast on your list. Shop now and spread joy this season with the gift of relaxation and happiness.', 1, 1, '2024-05-24 00:26:59', '2024-05-24 00:26:59', NULL),
(68, 'Gift Ideas', 'gift-ideas', 'product', 'Discover the perfect gift for cannabis enthusiasts with our curated selection. From premium strains to sleek smoking accessories, elevate any occasion with our handpicked assortment. Whether it\'s for a seasoned connoisseur or a newbie explorer, find unique and thoughtful gifts that celebrate the world of marijuana.', 1, 1, '2024-05-24 00:27:24', '2024-05-24 00:27:24', NULL),
(69, 'Winter Wonderland', 'winter-wonderland', 'product', 'Indulge in a frosty euphoria with Winter Wonderland, a premium strain that blankets the mind in a serene, snowy haze. Its frosty buds offer a crisp, piney aroma, while its soothing effects transport users to a tranquil, wintry landscape. Embrace the chill and let Winter Wonderland guide you to a blissful escape.', 1, 1, '2024-05-24 00:28:10', '2024-05-24 00:28:10', NULL),
